Thou born like a beatiful flower

waits for twinkle breeze blowing over

Please pick up a summer's affair

to insist on seeking sweet lover



Be not miserable，and  don't despair

when gloomy sunshine remains under cover

Keep smile and smiling charming forever

till thy lover returns with honor




炎热的夏季即将到来，沉睡的心是否也躁动不安?放眼天际，阳光也许为阴霾所遮盖，处于混沌不明的状态，但请别叹息，终有一天，在闪光的风中摇曳着迷人的微笑，你的未来……

注：试水英诗，可能会出现语法错误，若有不妥之处劳烦指正，不胜感激。
